<section id="download" class="w-full py-16 px-4 md:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold mb-4 text-center">Изтегли RAYDAR</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
      Започнете с RAYDAR днес и изпробвайте мощта на проследяването на лъчи.
    </p>
    
    <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm p-8 md:p-10">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between">
        <div class="mb-6 md:mb-0">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">RAYDAR v0.2.0: Performance Update</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 mb-4">Последна стабилна версия за Linux</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-white" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              BVH за CPU визуализация (до 2х по-бързо)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-white" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              GPU ускорение с Vulkan
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-white" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Графичен редактор на сцени
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-white" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Примитиви: сфери и кубове
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-white" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Дифузни, спекуларни, метални и стъклени материали
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4">
          <a 
            href="https://github.com/bvpav/raydar/releases/download/v0.2.0/raydar-v0.2.0-linux-x86_64.tar.gz" 
            class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-primary-600 font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-opacity-90 flex items-center justify-center transition-all transform hover:scale-105 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
